{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Fund more affordable, accessible housing for families with disabled children",
        "additional_details": "We think many face overcrowding, long waits for adaptations, and financial hardship. We urge the Government to fund more inclusive housing projects, to support local authorities to build homes specifically for families with disabled children. We believe every child deserves a safe, suitable home to thrive. Let this be their future.",
        "background": "Create a national fund for affordable, accessible housing for families raising disabled children across the UK. We believe thousands of families with disabled children live in unsuitable or unsafe housing, paying sky high rents to private landlords.",
